import react from 'react';
import React, {Component} from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router} from 'react-router-dom'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import './index.css'

ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <Router>
            <App />
        </Router>
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById('root')
    );
